<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-5810] Calling static method from subclass using super creates StackOverFlow</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-5810</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Don&apos;t know whether calling super from a static method is supposed to compile. But it does in IDEA IC-122.519 EAP using Groovy 2.0.5 and runs into an endless loop.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;@CompileStatic
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;A {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; foo() {
        print(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;A&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
    }
}

@CompileStatic
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;B &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; A {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; foo() {
        A.foo() &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// compiles and prints &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;AB&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;super&lt;/span&gt;.foo() &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// compiles and creates StackOverFlow
&lt;/span&gt;        print(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;B&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
    }

    def &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; main(args)
    {
        B.foo()
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
