                            <comment id="14473455" author="oliver_plow" created="Tue, 20 Nov 2012 17:05:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;At home with IntelliJ IDEA CE 122.694 EAP it does not compile. Not with Groovy 2.0.5 nor with 1.8.8. Sorry for any trouble caused if in the end it is caused by IDEA IC-122.519 EAP. The versions of IDEA 12 EAP can be downloaded from here: &lt;a href=&quot;http://confluence.jetbrains.com/display/IDEADEV/IDEA+12+EAP&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://confluence.jetbrains.com/display/IDEADEV/IDEA+12+EAP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14473538" author="melix" created="Fri, 30 Nov 2012 02:53:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As as sidenote, this problem is not specific to &lt;tt&gt;@CompileStatic&lt;/tt&gt;. Dynamic Groovy has the very same problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
